35:33.560 --> 35:36.360
Likewise, this is not an assessment.

35:36.360 --> 35:44.240
Core SGP uses CASP data and repurposes it in a novel way.

35:44.240 --> 35:50.440
As with Lexile-Quantile, Core is not an assessment to be approved, but rather a way of using

35:50.440 --> 35:56.520
the underlying data.

